My level bonus : (52-7)/3 = 45/3 = 15<br>
My Magic Number : (2 x 25) + 15 = 50 + 15 = 65<br>
<br>
Anyone care to notice what number the tall red bar hovers over? oh, look : 65. Notice where the shortest red bar is? The one I hit for like 0.01% of the time? Hey look, its at 99, my MAX dmg.<br>
<br>
Oh, and what does STR affect? Max dmg. and how is max dmg calculated? let's see...<br>
<br>
Max Damage (MAX) = (((Str + Wpn Skill)/100) x Wpn Dmg) + level bonus<br>
<br>
